question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Hoeveel mensen woonden er in de gemeente Odense, Denemarken op 1 juli 2022?
answer: Op 1 juli 2022 woonden er in de gemeente Odense, Denemarken, ongeveer 206.305 mensen.
answer_translated_eng: As of 1 July 2022, there were about 206,305 people living in Odense Municipality, Denmark.
